| 🔴 Critical | 1 | Split + LINQ + Join compound allocation in word truncator |
| 🟡 Moderate | 3 | Double alloc on right-truncate; List\<char\>[] linear scan; unsealed classes |
| ℹ️ Info | 0 | — |

